																					<h6 class="pb-3  font-medium text-base uppercase"><a class="dg-category text-lightgray" href="https://abilityoptions.org.au/category/news-media/news/" title="News">News</a><span class="dg-category text-black pl-4"  title="Date">11 August 2021</span></h6>
										<h3 class="pb-5 text-black font-black text-3xl"><a href="https://abilityoptions.org.au/seabreeze-and-bonville-new-mid-north-coast-respite-homes-for-people-with-disability-now-open/" title="Seabreeze and Bonville – New Mid-North Coast Respite Homes for people with disability now open">Seabreeze and Bonville – New Mid-North Coast Respite Homes for people with disability now open</a></h3>
										<p class="pb-5 text-black font-medium text-lg">Ability Options has re-opened their Seabreeze and Bonville Respite Homes in Port Macquarie and Coffs Harbour, following COVID-19 challenges of 2020 which led to an unforeseen year-long closure without Respite Services in the area. Respite Services provide short-term accommodation for people with disability and their carers to relax, or simply take a short break. This [&hellip;]</p>
										<a href="https://abilityoptions.org.au/seabreeze-and-bonville-new-mid-north-coast-respite-homes-for-people-with-disability-now-open/" class="uppercase inline-block text-black font-black text-lg border-b-2 border-green"> Read more </a>
									</div>
								</div>
															<div class="category_box1  bg-grey-light border-l-8 border-solid border-green p-6 mb-6 ">

									<div class="category_titlebox inline-block align-top w-full">
																					<h6 class="pb-3  font-medium text-base uppercase"><a class="dg-category text-lightgray" href="https://abilityoptions.org.au/category/news-media/news/" title="News">News</a><span class="dg-category text-black pl-4"  title="Date">16 July 2021</span></h6>
										<h3 class="pb-5 text-black font-black text-3xl"><a href="https://abilityoptions.org.au/mutual-obligation-update/" title="Mutual Obligations Update">Mutual Obligations Update</a></h3>
										<p class="pb-5 text-black font-medium text-lg">Mutual Obligation Requirements have been temporarily suspended until Tuesday 3 August 2021. This extended suspension of requirements applies to job seekers and participants with mutual obligation requirements across employment services programs − jobactive, ParentsNext, and DES. This applies throughout the LGAs of Bayside, Blue Mountains, Canada Bay, Central Coast, City of Sydney, Greater Sydney, Inner [&hellip;]</p>
										<a href="https://abilityoptions.org.au/mutual-obligation-update/" class="uppercase inline-block text-black font-black text-lg border-b-2 border-green"> Read more </a>
									</div>
								</div>
															<div class="category_box1  bg-grey-light border-l-8 border-solid border-green p-6 mb-6 ">

									<div class="category_titlebox inline-block align-top w-full">
																					<h6 class="pb-3  font-medium text-base uppercase"><a class="dg-category text-lightgray" href="https://abilityoptions.org.au/category/news-media/news/" title="News">News</a><span class="dg-category text-black pl-4"  title="Date">13 July 2021</span></h6>
										<h3 class="pb-5 text-black font-black text-3xl"><a href="https://abilityoptions.org.au/temporary-site-closures-due-to-covid/" title="Temporary site closures due to COVID">Temporary site closures due to COVID</a></h3>
										<p class="pb-5 text-black font-medium text-lg">Due to the Sydney lock down and the heightened exposure sites in the South West Sydney, we will be temporarily closing the following offices until Friday the 16th July 2021, with a decision on extending these temporary closures to be made at the end of the week depending on circumstances. Auburn Parramatta Merrylands Fairfield Cabramatta [&hellip;]</p>
										<a href="https://abilityoptions.org.au/temporary-site-closures-due-to-covid/" class="uppercase inline-block text-black font-black text-lg border-b-2 border-green"> Read more </a>
